import './SubmitPage.css' import { calculateResortsDriving } from '../scripts/drivingTimeLogic'; import Results from './Results'; import PossibleTrip from '../components/PossibleTrip'; function SubmitPage({ data }) { const resorts = calculateResortsDriving(data.Region, data["Zip Code"]); return (

Your Submission Details

Region: {data.Region || "N/A"}
Fly or not {data["Willing to fly?"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Stay: {data.Stay || "N/A"}
Zip Code: {data["Zip Code"] || "N/A"}
Number of Guests: {data["Number of Guests"] || "N/A"}
Epic Pass: {data["Epic Pass"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Ikon Pass: {data["Ikon Pass"] ? "Yes" : "No"}
Start Date: {data["Start Date"] || "N/A"}
End Date: {data["End Date"] || "N/A"}

Zip Code to Latitude/Longitude

{resorts.length > 0 ? (

All valid resorts in the area:

{resorts.map((element, index) => (

{element.name} | Estimated Driving Time: {element.drivingTime}

))}
) : (

Invalid zip code. try again

)}
) } export default SubmitPage;
